# Flutter TikTok-Style Video App Project Plan

## 1. Project Overview

This project is a TikTok-style vertical short-video application built with Flutter.

The main objective is to create a smooth full-screen vertical video feed where users can swipe up and down to watch videos fetched from the Pexels API.

The app will focus first on video feed performance, clean architecture, maintainable code structure, and stable video player lifecycle management.

