4. Add crash monitoring
5. Test release build
6. Test low-end Android devices
7. Test iOS devices
8. Test poor network
9. Test fast swiping
10. Test memory usage
11. Add privacy policy
12. Add terms of service
13. Review Pexels API usage rules
