---

## 26. Final Architecture Recommendation

The final MVP architecture should be:

```txt
Flutter UI
  ↓
Bloc
  ↓
Use Case
  ↓
Repository
  ↓
Remote Data Source
  ↓
Dio
  ↓
Pexels API
```

Video lifecycle should be separate:

```txt
VideoFeedPage
  ↓
VideoPlayerManager
  ↓
media_kit Player
```

This separation keeps the app maintainable, testable, and safer against video memory crashes.

---

## 27. Final MVP Priority

The most important MVP goal is not to build all TikTok features.

The most important MVP goal is:

```txt
Prove that Flutter + media_kit can deliver a smooth vertical video feed with safe memory usage.
```

After that is stable, social features and backend features can be added progressively.
